{"lemma":"ذِهْنِ","slug":"ذِهْنِ","root":"ذ.ه.ن","root_slug":"ذ-ه-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ذ-ه-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n14134","n14135","n14136","n14137"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B0%D9%90%D9%87%D9%92%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mind","examples":[{"text":"Al-Mutanabbi\nوَلَيْسَ يَصِحُّ فِي الْأَذْهَانِ شَيْءٌ / إِذَا ٱحْتَاجَ النَّهَارُ إِلَى دَلِيلِ\nwalaysa yaṣiḥḥu fī l-ʾaḏhāni šayʾun / ʾiḏā ḥtāja n-nahāru ʾilā dalīli","english":"(please add an English translation of this quotation)"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"intellect"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ðihn/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n14134","headword_ar":"ذَهِنَ","root":"*hn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (MA, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ihonN","text_ar":"ذِهْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahanN","text_ar":"ذَهَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MA, KL,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, intelligent, possessed of understanding, sagacious, acute, skilful, knowing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, KL, PS, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endowed with a retentive mind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL, PS.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai*ohano A_ilaY maA A^aquwlu","text_ar":"اِذْهَنْ اـِلَى مَا اَقُولُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Understand thou what I say."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa laA ya*ohanu $ayoy^FA","text_ar":"هُوَ لَا يَذْهَنُ شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He does not understand anything."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahinotu ka*aA","text_ar":"ذَهِنْتُ كَذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wa ka*aA","text_ar":"وَ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I understood such and such things."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahinotu Eano ka*aA","text_ar":"ذَهِنْتُ عَنْ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I understood from such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAhananiY fa*ahanotuhu","text_ar":"ذَاهَنَنِى فَذَهَنْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 3. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahananiY Eanohu","text_ar":"ذَهَنَنِى عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*ohananiY","text_ar":"اَذْهَنَنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisota*ohananiY","text_ar":"اِسْتَذْهَنَنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, made me to forget it; diverted me from remembering it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahalaniY","text_ar":"ذَهَلَنِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eanohu","text_ar":"عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*ohalaniY","text_ar":"اَذْهَلَنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uhina","text_ar":"ذُهِنَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Memory,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"understanding, escaped him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"left him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.)"}],"source_refs":["MA","TA","KL","PS"]},{"entry_id":"n14135","headword_ar":"ذِهْنٌ","root":"*hn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, Msb, K, &c.) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahanN","text_ar":"ذَهَنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Intellect, intelligence, understanding, sagacity, acuteness, skill,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knowledge;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqolN","text_ar":"عَقْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fahomN","text_ar":"فَهْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiTonapN","text_ar":"فِطْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*akaA='N","text_ar":"ذَكَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retentiveness of mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"memory:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, * S, * K:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a faculty of the soul, provided for the acquisition of the several species of knowledge, including the external and internal senses:"},{"kind":"text","text":"strength thereof is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*akaA='N","text_ar":"ذَكَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and a good quality thereof for the forming ideas of the things that present themselves to it is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiTonapN","text_ar":"فِطْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*ohaAnN","text_ar":"اَذْهَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, K. *) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AijoEalo *ihonaka A_ilaY ka*aA waka*aA","text_ar":"اِجْعَلْ ذِهْنَكَ اـِلَى كَذَا وَكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Apply thine intellect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to such and such things"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [Both are also inf. ns.: see 1, first sentence.] ―         -b2-  Also, the former, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strength:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K:) pl. as above. (K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA birijolaY~a *ihonN","text_ar":"مَا بِرِجْلَىَّ ذِهْنٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in my legs any strength to walk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa mino A^aholi Al*~ihoni","text_ar":"هُوَ مِنْ اَهْلِ الذِّهْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^a*ohaAni","text_ar":"الاَذْهَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is of those endowed with strength"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of body:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of those endowed with intelligence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intelligent faculties"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA raA^ayotu biAlA_ibili *ihonFA","text_ar":"مَا رَاَيْتُ بِالاـِبِلِ ذِهْنًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I saw not, in the camels, fat"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strength."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) ―         -b3-  Also (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pith"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"niqoY","text_ar":"نِقْى"},{"kind":"text","text":") of canes, or reeds. (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahinN","text_ar":"ذَهِنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K","JK","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n14136","headword_ar":"ذَهَنٌ","root":"*hn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n14137","headword_ar":"ذَهِنٌ","root":"*hn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ihonN","text_ar":"ذِهْنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Intelligent, possessed of understanding, sagacious, acute, skilful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knowing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endowed with a retentive mind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] each [said to be] a possessive epithet, [signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possessing"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ihon","text_ar":"ذِهْن"},{"kind":"text","text":", though the former is agreeable with a general rule as part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahina","text_ar":"ذَهِنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] applied to a man; the latter app. changed [or contracted] from the former. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}